\begin_layout Standard
There are two types of capacity in software development;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Capacity to innovate and develop new features (ex: velocity)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Capacity to deliver volume of service (ex measured in users per minute)
