\begin_layout Standard
Volume is a problem that can be solved easily with resources, but capacity
 to develop new features and innovate is a hard problem that can sometimes
 not even be solved by resources.
 Thus, capacity to innovate is a constraint that development companies need
 to optimize their operations around.
 It follows that a key challenge is to determine what products and features
 to invest in.
 Even in cases where development capacity is not limited, this is an important
 challenge as customer attention and interest are limited.
\end_layout

